item.title: CVE-2017-2632|2024-08-05T14:02:06.842Z -- red%20hat -- cfme
item.description: A logic error in valid_role() in CloudForms role validation before 5.7.1.3 could allow a tenant administrator to create groups with a higher privilege level than the tenant administrator should have. This would allow an attacker with tenant administration access to elevate privileges.
